parse_perf_script.py
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
parses the output of "perf script", extracts specified events' data and save
the data to separate files one per each event in json format


make_perf_json.py
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
parses events using "perf record -p <pid> -e <events> record <seconds>" command
and saves the parsed data to file in json format


show_histogram.py
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
visualizes the event data provided  in form of hystogramm. As an input file it
uses files produced by make_perf_json.py and parse_perf_script.py
